title: ElTrendnor Rigby 11/8: University of Austin, Jaylen Brown, Jeff Bezos, Nation of Islam, Astroworld, Overrated Foods
itunes:title: ElTrendnor Rigby 11/8: University of Austin, Jaylen Brown, Jeff Bezos, Nation of Islam, Astroworld, Overrated Foods
description:
In this edition of ElTrendnor Rigby, Jack and Miles discuss 'University of Austin' launching with a controversial board of directors, the Jaylen Brown/Ben Simmons trade rumors, Lauren Sanchez drooling over Leo in front of Bezos at LACMA, Marjorie Taylor Greene seeing 'common ground' with Nation of Islam, the Astroworld debacle, and which foods are overrated.
